#. Translators: Label shown when a video or image has failed to load.
#: data/resources/ui/page.blp:61
msgid ""
"Could not display the file.\n"
"\n"
"If you're running Identity under Flatpak, note that opening files by drag-"
"and-drop and by pasting may not work."
msgstr ""
"Impussibil visualizâ il file.\n"
"\n"
"Se tu stâs eseguint Identitât di un Flatpak, viôt che al podarès no funzionâ "
"la vierzidure di files cul \"strissine e mole\" e tacantju."

