#~ msgid ""
#~ "This release adds pixelated display for zoomed-in images and videos, "
#~ "improves format support and fixes several issues."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Cheste publicazion e zonte la visualizazion a pixels pes imagjins e pai "
#~ "videos ingrandîts, e miore il supuart ai formâts e al comede diviers "
#~ "problemis."

#~ msgid "Zoomed-in images and videos are now pixelated rather than blurry."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Lis imagjins e i videos ingrandîts cumò a son a pixels invezit che fûr "
#~ "fûc."

#~ msgid "Fixed memory usage not decreasing upon closing images and videos."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Comedade mancjade diminuzion de utilizazion de memorie al sierâ di "
#~ "imagjins e videos."

#~ msgid "Improved UI responsiveness with many open files."
#~ msgstr "Reativitât miorade de interface grafiche cun tancj files vierts."

#~ msgid "Improved performance on AV1 videos."
#~ msgstr "Prestazions mioradis sui videos AV1."

#~ msgid "Added support for WebP images."
#~ msgstr "Zontât supuart pes imagjins WebP."

#~ msgid "Fixed display of semitransparent images and videos."
#~ msgstr "Comedade visualizazion di imagjins e videos in semi-trasparence."

#~ msgid "Fixed display of 16-bit color images."
#~ msgstr "Comedade visualizazion di imagjins a 16-bit di colôrs."

#~ msgid "Removed panning from the touchpad pinch zoom gesture."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Al è stât gjavât il spostament contignûts su schermi dal mot pal touchpad "
#~ "pal zoom cu la piçade."

